<h3> Top 1 Sichuan hot pot </h3>
<ul>
</lbr>
<img src="http://thewoksoflife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/hot-pot-13.jpg" align=sticky src="sichuan.jpg" widh="170" height="170"></h2>

<li>No matter during winter or summer, it is always my favorite</li>
<li>The ultimate party food
<li>Ingredients: fresh and potent Sichuan peppercorn, Sichuan chillies, ground chilles and many other kinds of chilies <a</br>
<li> sliced beef, pork, chicken, lamb, and all kinds of meat

